summary: Jon Snow from Game of Thrones preset slot file for RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]v2. Added jslot file for RM3[/size]

[size=4]This is not a mod (since I have no idea how to make one), just the preset slot file for RaceMenu[/size]

[b]Required mods:[/b]

Latest [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] (and it's requirements)
HD [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28363/?]Beards[/url]
[url=http://gamer-mods.ru/load/tes_v_skyrim/kosmeticheskie_mody/ks_hairdos_265_zhenskie_i_muzhskie_pricheski_v1_1/14-1-0-2506]KS Hairdos[/url] (this file seems to be have removed from NexusMods so the link is to a russian site)

[b]Installation:[/b]

Place file inÂ Skyrim -> Data -> SKSE -> Plugins -> CharGen -> Presets

Note! Change the filename to a number (0 ->, depending on your own .slot files)

Face mod used in pics: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27815/?]Fine Faces textures for men by Urshi[/url]
Body mod used in pics: [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/forum/index.php?topic=8263]SAM[/url] by Vectorplexus (incl. textures and armor used in pics)
Armor used in pic is Elven Light for [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/forum/index.php?topic=8263]SAM[/url]
author: Ixator
